Q7. Perform one-sample t-test and two-sample t-test.


R
Copy code
# One-sample t-test
t.test(data$Salary, mu = 50000)

# Two-sample t-test
t.test(Salary ~ Gender, data = data)
Hypothesis
One Sample
H0: Mean salary = 50000
H1: Mean salary ≠ 50000
Two Sample
H0: Male aur Female salary ka mean same hai
H1: Dono ka mean different hai
Interpretation:
p-value < 0.05 ho to null hypothesis reject ho jata hai.


